name: store test results
info:
This subflow stores the test result data in a text file.

## Inputs

 - flow.filepath (for the file path)
 - flow.maintopic (for the file name)
 - msg.topic (for the test name)
 - msg.payload (for the test results)

## Outputs
 - msg.filename (the full file name of the test results file)
 - msg.payload (the test results prepended with datetime and topic)

name: important notes
info:
Setup globals for the various flows, it is triggered on each deploy. You may want to disable this when developing new tests. This is done by unchecking the 'Inject once after x seconds' option in the Inject node.

## Global variables
 - The **localdir** folder is used to collect output and test results. 
 - The **email** address is used to send all email communication to the specified email address.
 - The **timezone** value is used for formatting date stamps for your local time zone.
